Text:"<s1384>					</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Aruna aitũ, tigagai gwĩtanga nĩ ũndũ o na ũrĩkũ: no rĩrĩ, </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>menyithagiai Ngai maũndũ marĩa mothe mwendaga, mũkĩmũhoyaga na mũkĩmũthaithaga,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> hamwe na kũmũcokeria ngatho.  Naguo thayũ wa Ngai, ũrĩa ũtangĩmenyeka ũrĩa ũtariĩ, </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>nĩ ũrĩikaragia ngoro cianyu o na gwĩciria kwanyu nakuo thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu. </s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> Na ngũrĩkĩrĩria atĩrĩ, ariũ a Ithe witũ, maũndũ o marĩa ma ma, namo marĩa matĩĩku, na ma kĩhooto,</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> na marĩa matheru, na marĩa mangĩendeka, o na marĩa me na ũhoreri-rĩ, ningĩ kũngĩrĩ na ũndũ wĩ mwagĩrĩru,</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384> kana ũndũ wa kũgathwo, maũndũ macio-rĩ, wĩciragiei ũhoro wamo.  Namo maũndũ marĩa mwerutire harĩ niĩ mũkĩmetĩkĩra,</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> na ningĩ mũkĩmaigua harĩ niĩ, na mũkĩmona, ĩkagai mo; nake Ngai mwene thayũ nĩ arĩikaraga na inyuĩ.</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani.
							</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>   Alleluya. Alleluya.</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ niĩ mũthabibũ, nĩ inyuĩ honge; ũrĩa ũikaire thĩinĩ wakwa,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> na niĩ ngaikara thĩinĩ wake, ũcio nĩ aciaraga maciaro maingĩ</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Alleluia</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ"},{Guid:"y9MKiZFOgU6WX/AF99k+VQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>			   
GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI THERU TA ŨRĨA YANDĨKĨTWO NĨ MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu nĩ erire Asacerdoti arĩa anene na Afarisei: Ta iguai ngerekano ingĩ: </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Kwarĩ mũndũ mwene mũciĩ wahandire mũgũnda wa mĩthabibũ, akĩũiriga, na akĩenja ihihĩro rĩa thabibũ o kũu thĩinĩ, na agĩaka rũtara,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> akĩũkomborithia arĩmi agĩthiĩ bũrũri ũngĩ.  Na hingo ya kũgetha  maciaro yakuhihĩria, akĩrekeria arĩmi acio ngombo ciake, ikaneo maciaro make. </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384> Na arĩmi acio makĩnyita ngombo ciake, makĩhũra ĩmwe, na ĩngĩ makĩmĩũraga, o na ĩngĩ makĩmĩhũra na mahiga. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384> Ningĩ agĩcoka akĩrekia ngombo ingĩ nyingĩ kũrĩ icio cia mbere: nao magĩciĩka o ũguo.  Thutha wa ũguo akĩmarekeria mũriũ,</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384> akiuga: Nĩ magaconokera mũrũ wakwa.  No arĩmi acio mona mũriũ, makĩĩrana atĩrĩ: Ũyũ nĩwe ũkegaĩrũo mũgũnda.  </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>Rekei tũmũũrage, tũkegwatĩre igai rĩake.  Magĩkĩmũnyita, makĩmwagararia rũgiri rũa mũgũnda , makĩmũũraga.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>  Rĩu-rĩ, rĩrĩa mwathani wa mũgũnda agacoka-rĩ, agagĩĩka arĩmi acio atĩa? Nao andũ makĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩ kũnina akamanina ũũru, andũ acio oru, na akomborithie arĩmi angĩ mũgũnda ũcio, </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>arĩa marĩmũneaga maciaro hĩndĩ yamo yakinya.  Nake Yesu akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Kaĩ mũtarĩ mwathoma Maandĩko-inĩ ũũ: </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384> Ihiga rĩrĩa rĩaregirũo nĩ aaki, nĩrĩo rĩtuĩkĩte o rĩrĩa inene rĩa koine: ũndũ ũcio woimire kwĩ Mwathani, </s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>na nĩ ũtũgegagia tũkĩwona? Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ũthamaki wa Ngai nĩ ũkarutwo kũrĩ inyuĩ,</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> ũheo rũrĩrĩ rũrĩa rũgaciaraga maciaro maguo.</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"INJIRI"},{Guid:"SBcJ/EeGrUC/IS56LyVbYg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>	
Ta reka nyinĩre ũrĩa mwendwa wakwa rũĩmbo rũake, ũcio nyendete  mũno, rũkoniĩ mũgũnda wake wa mĩthabibũ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>  Ũcio mwendwa wakwa aarĩ na mũgũnda wa mĩthabibũ kĩrĩma-inĩ handũ hanoru mũno, nake akĩũthiũrũrũkĩria mũtaro,</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> akĩũngania mahiga mothe marĩa maarĩ kuo, akĩmate, agĩcoka akĩhanda mũthemba wa mũthabibũ ũrĩa mwega gũkĩra ĩrĩa ĩngĩ,</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> agĩgĩaka mũthiringo wa nyũmba ndaya na igũrũ o kũu gatagatĩ kaguo, akĩenja handũ ha kũhihĩra thabibũ kũu thĩinĩ waguo;</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> agĩgĩikara ehokete atĩ mũgũnda ũcio nĩ ũgaciara thabibũ njega; no rĩrĩ, waciarire o thabibũ cia gĩthaka.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>  Rĩu-rĩ, inyuĩ andũ aya mũtũũraga Jerusalemu, o na inyuĩ andũ a Judea, ta tũtuithaniei cira, </s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>niĩ na mũgũnda ũcio wakwa wa mĩthabibũ.  Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩ ũndũ ũrĩkũ ũngĩagĩĩkirũo mũgũnda ũcio wa mĩthabibũ itaakĩwĩkire? </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Kũngĩkorũo nĩ ũguo-rĩ wagĩciarire thabibũ cia gĩthaka nĩkĩ, na niĩ ndũire ndĩĩhokete atĩ nĩ ũgaciara thabibũ njega?</s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Atĩrĩrĩ, rĩu ta kĩrekei ndĩmwĩre ũrĩa ngwĩka mũgũnda ũcio wakwa wa mĩthabibũ; nĩ kweheria ngweheria  rũgiri rũaguo,</s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> ndĩũrĩithie, njoke ‘tharie rũirigo rũaguo, ũrangwo na magũrũ, ndĩũtige wanangĩkĩte. </s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Naguo ndũgacoka gũcehwo mĩtĩ yaguo, kana ũrĩmwo, no nĩ kũmera ũrĩmeraga mĩtĩ ya mĩigua na ria ta cong’e;</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> ningĩ njathane njĩre matu atĩ mbura ndĩkanauurĩre.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> Nĩ gũkorũo mũgũnda wa mĩthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita nĩguo nyũmba ya Israeli,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> nao andũ a Juda nĩo mũtĩ ũrĩa mwega ekenagĩra nĩguo. Nake ehokaga atĩ nĩ arĩonaga cira wa kĩhooto;</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384> no rĩrĩ, ũhoro wa kũhinyanĩrĩria noguo onaga.  Ningĩ akehoka atĩ nĩ ekuona ũthingu; no rĩrĩ, kĩrĩro nokĩo aiguaga.</s>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><s1384>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"githomo kia mbere"},{Guid:"7p/E8pWGBkmoPOKUojQjlg",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>IHOYA KŨRĨ MŨTHURE JOSEPH</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Wee Mũkeni Josebu, Mũikaria na mũreri wa Mũhono kia witũ, Mũthuuri wa Maria Thingi.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>Ngai nĩa kwĩhokeire ũramati wa Mwana wake; Na Maria Mũtheru akĩiga mwĩhoko wake harĩ We;</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384> Na nĩ harĩ we Kristũ atuĩkire mũndũ.  
Mũkeni Josebu, Tuĩka harĩ ithuĩ, ithe witũ, Na ũtũtongorie njĩra-inĩ ya ũtũũro.  </s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Tũhoere kũrĩ Ngai, wega mũtheria, tha na ũcamba, Na ũtũgitĩre maũru-inĩ moothe. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Nĩgũtuĩke guo.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{Transition:0},Background:{Transition:18}},
Text:"IHOYA KŨRĨ MŨTHURE JOSEPH
"},{Guid:"tXOncxng3UiEcxHRGXbfeA",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia makuhani wakuu na wazee wa baraza,  \"Sikilizeni mfano mwingine. Kulikuwa na mtu mwenye shamba. </s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384> Naye alipanda mizabibu, akalizungushia wigo, akachimba mahali pa kukamulia matunda, akajenga kilindo, akapangisha wakulima, akasafiri. </s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>Kulipokaribia majira ya kukomaa matunda, akawatuma watumishi wake kwa wale wakulima, wapokee matunda yake.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Wakulima wakawakamata watumishi wake, mmoja wao wakampiga, mwingine wakamwua, na mtu wa tatu wakamtupia mawe. </s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>Akawatuma tena watumishi wengine wengi kuliko wa kwanza. Kumbe, wakawatendea vile vile sawa na wale wa kwanza.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mwisho akamtuma mwanawe aende kwao, akisema, Watamjali mwanangu.\"</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384> Lakini wale wakulima walipomwona mwana, wakasemezana, 'Huyu ni mrithi. Haya tumwue na kutwaa urithi wake. </s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Wakamkamata, wakamtupa nje ya shamba la mizabibu, wakamwua. </s>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1384> Basi, bwana wa shamba la mizabibu atawatenda wale wakulima nini atakapokuja kwao?\" </s>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1384>Wakamwambia, \"Hao wabaya atawaangamiza vibaya, na shamba la mizabibu atawapangisha wakulima wengine watakaomrudishia matunda wakati wake.\"</s>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1384>Yesu akawaambia, \"Hamjasoma bado katika Maandiko:</s>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1384>\"Jiwe walilolikataa waashi limepata kuwa jiwe kuu la pembeni.</s>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1384> Hayo yamefanywa na Bwana, nayo ni ajabu machoni mwetu?\"
Kwa hiyo nawaambieni,</s>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1384> ufalme wa Mungu utaondolewa kwenu, na utatolewa kwa taifa jingine lenye kuzaa matunda yake.\"</s>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1384>Injili ya Bwana.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
Text:"Somo la Injili "},{Guid:"htnRxvgosU2p/z+0LmOXZw",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Mimi ni mzabibu, mimi ni mzabibu
Nanyi mu matawi yangu *2</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384>    Kaeni ndani yangu, nami ndani yenu -
    Kwani mu matawi nami kweli ni mzabibu</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384>    Nje yangu mimi hamuwezi kuzaa kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>    Tawi lizaalo, lizidi kuzaa kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>    Furaha yangu iwe, ndani yenu kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>    Ombeni lolote, nanyi mtapewa kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>    Amri yangu ndiyo, mpate kupendana kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>    Niliwachagua, muwe rafiki zangu kwani . . .</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>    Zaeni matunda, yapate kukaa kwani </s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
