Text:"SOMO LA PILI "},{Guid:"xsCirnB1xUGY3dy0uPQPQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<s1384>Mũgũnda wa Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩguo kĩrĩndĩ gĩake.</s>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1384></s><s1846>1.Warehire mũthabibũ ũrutĩte Misri, ũkĩrutũrũra ndũrĩrĩ, ũkĩũhanda arĩ guo.  Ũgĩtambia honge ciaguo kinya o iria-inĩ, na thuna ciaguo ũgĩikinyia o rũũĩ.</s>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1384></s><s1846>Mũgũnda wa Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩgu</s><s1384>o kĩrĩndĩ gĩake.</s>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1384>2.	Nĩ ũndũ kĩ ũkiunangĩte njirigo ciaguo, ũgagĩĩtuagĩrũo nĩ arĩa othe ehĩtũkĩri na njĩra? Ngũrũe ĩrĩa  yumaga kĩrĩti nĩ ĩũgũmagia, na nĩ ũrĩĩkaga nĩ nyamũ cia werũ.</s>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgũnda wa Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩguo kĩrĩndĩ gĩake.</s>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1384>3.	Tũcokerere, Ngai mwene mbũtũ cia ita, twagũthaitha: ikia maitho wĩ kũu igũrũ, wone, ũkĩroore mũthabibũ ũyũ.  O guo mũtĩ ũrĩa guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo kwahandire, ruo rũhonge rũrĩa werereire nĩ bata waku mwene.</s>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgũnda wa Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩguo kĩrĩndĩ gĩake.</s>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1384>4.	Na ithuĩ-rĩ, tũtikahũndũka tũtigane nawe: tũriũkie, na nĩ tũgũtũũra tũthathayagia rĩĩtwa rĩaku.  Mwathani Ngai mwene mbũtũ cia ita, tũcokererie; tũma ũthiũ  waku ware, na nĩ tũkũhonoka.</s>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1384>Mũgũnda wa Mũthabibũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani nĩguo kĩrĩndĩ gĩake.</s>"}],Style:{Body:{VerticalAlignment:1,Transition:0}},
